tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE User_Feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    virtual_assistant_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    assistant_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE AssistantRating (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    assistant_id INT,
    total_ratings INT,
    average_rating FLOAT,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
  feedback_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  assistant_id INT NOT NULL,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    assistant_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE AssistantDetails (
    assistant_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    assistant_name VARCHAR(255),
    assistant_type VARCHAR(50),
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE UserRatings (
  rating_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  assistant_id INT,
  rating_value INT,
  feedback_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE Users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name VARCHAR(50),
  last_name VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);
